Bug fixes and optimizations.

Thank you for reporting bugs to us! We ve corrected some things from your feedback: The resume playback feature got lost. We put signs all over town and now it s back home. The app is now quicker! Fixed crashing around video playback because that shouldn t happen. Other improvements and tuning. SKIP AHEAD: Scrub forward to where you left off without having to watch all the ads in between CW SEED: Easy access to every episode of Whose Line EVER and original comedies on our free CW Seed companion app
Bug fixes and optimizations.

SKIP AHEAD: We got your feedback and now you can jump to any part of the episode you want to watch BUG FIXES: We obliterated any code critter that was affecting video playback CW SEED: Easy access to over 200 episodes of Whose Line and original comedies on our free CW Seed companion app

We ve listened to your feedback and have made a number of fixes and improvements in this update including: Fixed issue where video does not stay in landscape when launch in landscape is selected Fixed issue where audio continued playing after exiting video Addressed problem where episodes were ending early during commercial breaks Made further improvements to stability and performance

New in 2.2.1089 Optimizations and bug fixes New in 2.1.1083 This complete redesign of the app for iOS 8 makes it easier than ever to get to the shows you want to watch Our video player got a suped up more reliable engine A simplified schedule page lets you know when your favorite shows air Streamlined photo galleries with more pictures of ridiculously attractive CW stars Access to exclusive CW Seed digital comedies like the Veronica Mars spin off Play It Again Dick and the award winning Husbands We eradicated some bugs and left traps out for stragglers
